reviewText: Berryz and C-ute the top 2 of Japan singer / dancer / concert performers. And ... Both of these groups become music-and-costumed veteans of more then 10 years from junior high to college! Fab! Flew to Tokyo in 2008-09-10 and saw both super-talent girls! Awsome.
I had seen pieces of the performance on youtube. This is a fun concert and I enjoyed every minute of the show
